        <p>Drop in Crime Slows</p>
        <p>The double-digit decline in crime that New York City has enjoyed in the last  two years is slowing, police statistics show. Page 21.</p>
        <p>Greer Garson Dies</p>
        <p>The actress who starred in some of the sleekest, most sentimental movies of the 1940's, including "Mrs. Miniver," was 92. Page 27.</p>
        <p>Cranking the Hands of Time</p>
        <p>Resetting the giant Colgate Clock in Jersey City for daylight saving time is  no simple task. Page 26.</p>
